The Many Deaths of Laila Starr is the latest modern classic published under Boom Studios, which seems to be firing on all cylinder lately. Written by acclaimed writer Ram V, with gorgeous art by the incomparable Filipe Andrade, Many Deaths is a deep look at the human experience, our relationship with death, and what it truly means to live forever. Join us as we tackle this emotional roller coaster of a story from beginning to end on the latest episode of the Major Issues Podcast! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

